## ğŸ® Core Game Concepts

1. **Three City Columns** - Mild â†’ Moderate â†’ Critical (left to right)
2. **Scouting** - Hidden cities must be revealed before treating
3. **Treating** - Moves cities LEFT toward cure
4. **Toxic Waste** - Deck pollution from outbreaks (lose condition)
5. **No Cubes** - Column position IS the infection level

