## ğŸ› ï¸ Development Guidelines

### Before Making Changes
1. Check `doc/` for existing specs
2. Maintain consistency with documented mechanics
3. Keep the solo-game focus (no multiplayer)

### Code Style
- Vanilla JS (no frameworks yet)
- CSS custom properties in `:root`
- SVG cards at 180x250 viewBox

### When Adding Features
1. Update `doc/game-design.md` if mechanics change
2. Update `doc/card-art-assets.md` if adding new card types
3. Follow existing card SVG patterns

